value.name: MONOEYES「Dim The Lights Tour 2017 at Studio Coast」
value.original_name: MONOEYES「Dim The Lights Tour 2017 at Studio Coast」
value.overview:
MONOEYES' nationwide tour Dim The Lights Tour 2017 took place in 2017.

The 29 shows were a great success, and the Tokyo Shinkiba Studio Coast leg of the tour is now on air!

Tickets for all shows were SOLD OUT as soon as they went on sale, and we present you with a rare glimpse of this rare performance.
